reviews.review_text: 2 Beatle Cover Encores in a Row! Thanx Keith.  I've been waiting 15 years to hear this.  The sound is kind of distant and the show average I'm still happy to get this.  I like the vocals at the end of He's Gone, two helpings, and a nice Stella.  Rain sounds good.  Check it out first.  Peace
